The caption says "One month and still in the honeymoon phase".

The image shows a woman, presumably sharnaalee, in a wedding dress holding a bouquet of white flowers. The caption says "Happiness is being married to your best friend."

The image shows a couple, presumably tomsimak and sharnaalee, standing on a balcony with a view of Coolum Beach in Queensland. They are holding a fluffy cat. The caption mentions that they have moved into a new home in Queensland.
The image shows sharnaalee and a man (presumably @mrshaunusmaximus) celebrating her 40th birthday. There are balloons and a "40" sign in the background. She is holding a glass of champagne.
